---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: "/"
title: "G Flexipack — Flexible Packaging Manufacturer · Bharuch, India"
description: "Custom-printed flexible packaging from Bharuch, Gujarat. Fourteen pouch formats, 9-colour rotogravure print, ISO 9001:2015, 300+ metric ton/month capacity, MOQ 500kg."
pageImage: "/assets/images/standup.png"
---
{% import "partials/icons.njk" as icons %}

  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <section class="hh-hero" id="hero">
    <div class="hh-hero-inner">
      <div class="hh-hero-text">
        <p class="hh-eyebrow">Flexible packaging · Est. {{ site.founded }}</p>
        <h1 class="hh-hero-title">Packaging built for <em>shelf impact.</em></h1>
        <p class="hh-hero-sub">
          G Flexipack is a Bharuch-based flexible packaging manufacturer producing custom-printed pouches
          for food, beverage, pharma, personal care, agrochemical, industrial and household brands -
          14 formats, printed, laminated and converted under one roof.
        </p>
        <div class="hh-hero-ctas">
          <a class="cta cta-primary" href="#inquiry">Get a quote <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hh-marquee" aria-label="Formats we print and sectors we pack for">
        <!-- Column A — FORMATS -->
        <div class="hh-col">
          <div class="hh-track hh-down">
            {% for p in products %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:#3b2a20; --bandc:#eae0cd; --band-text:#3b2a20;"><img class="hh-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ p.image }}.png" alt="{{ p.name }}" loading="lazy" /><span class="hh-tag">{{ p.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}{% for p in products %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:#3b2a20; --bandc:#eae0cd; --band-text:#3b2a20;"><img class="hh-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ p.image }}.png" alt="{{ p.name }}" loading="lazy" /><span class="hh-tag">{{ p.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Column B — SECTORS -->
        <div class="hh-col">
          <div class="hh-track hh-up">
            {% for s in industries %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:{{ s.accent }}; --bandc:#3b2a20; --band-text:#eae0cd;"><img class="hh-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ s.image }}.png" alt="{{ s.short }} sector packaging" loading="lazy" /><span class="hh-tag">{{ s.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}{% for s in industries %}<article class="hh-tile" style="--bg:{{ s.accent }}; --bandc:#3b2a20; --band-text:#eae0cd;"><img class="hh-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ s.image }}.png" alt="{{ s.short }} sector packaging" loading="lazy" /><span class="hh-tag">{{ s.short }}</span></article>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="hh-meta" aria-label="At a glance">
    <div>
      <strong>ISO <em>Certified</em>.</strong>
      9001:2015 quality management system, audited across every stage of production.
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong><em>300+ MT</em> capacity.</strong>
      Printing, lamination and pouching lines running at scale, in-house.
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Exporting to <em>10+ countries</em>.</strong>
      Sea freight coordinated worldwide, with full export documentation.
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ WELCOME ============ -->
  <section class="sec welcome" id="about-teaser">
    <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
      <p class="sec-eyebrow">Welcome to our company</p>
      <h2 class="sec-title">Quality packaging, <em>since {{ site.founded }}.</em></h2>
      <p class="sec-lead">
        G Flexipack is a Bharuch-based flexible packaging manufacturer producing custom-printed
        pouches for food, beverage, pharma, personal care, agrochemical, industrial and household
        brands — 14 formats, printed, laminated and converted under one roof.
      </p>
      <p style="text-align:center; margin-top:26px;"><a class="cta cta-ghost" href="/about/">More about us <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ VISION & MISSION ============ -->
  <section class="sec vm" aria-label="Vision and mission">
    <div class="vm-grid">
      <div class="vm-panel" style="--vc:#b25c2e;" data-reveal>
        <span class="vm-label">Our Vision</span>
        <p class="vm-quote">To be the flexible packaging <em>partner of choice</em> for brands that care how their product lands on shelf.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vm-panel" style="--vc:#7a6e3f;" data-reveal>
        <span class="vm-label">Our Mission</span>
        <p class="vm-quote">Design and print custom pouches that <em>protect the product</em> and represent the brand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ TICKER DIVIDER ============ -->
  <div class="ticker" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="ticker-track">
      {% for i in [1, 2] %}<div class="ticker-set">
        <span class="ticker-item">Upto <em>9-colour</em> printing</span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">Food-grade <em>barrier films</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">ISO <em>9001:2015</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item"><em>300+ metric ton</em> capacity</span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item"><em>60,000+ sq ft</em> climate-controlled plant</span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
        <span class="ticker-item">Exporting to <em>10+ countries</em></span><span class="ticker-star">✻</span>
      </div>{% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ OUR PRODUCTS ============ -->
  <section id="products-teaser">
    <div class="sec">
      <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
        <p class="sec-eyebrow">Our products</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title">Fourteen formats, <em>printed to spec.</em></h2>
        <p class="sec-lead">Custom dimensions, laminate structures, barrier levels and full-colour rotogravure print — all produced in-house.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rail-wrap">
      <div class="rail" id="formatRail">
        {% for p in products %}<a class="r-card" href="/products/{{ p.slug }}/">
          <span class="r-fig" style="--tbg:{{ p.tbg }};"><img src="/assets/images/{{ p.image }}.png" alt="{{ p.name }}" loading="lazy" /></span>
          <span class="r-body"><span class="r-name">{{ p.name }}</span><span class="r-link">View details →</span></span>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="rail-btns">
        <button class="rail-btn" id="railPrev" aria-label="Previous formats"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="15 5 8 12 15 19"></polyline></svg></button>
        <button class="rail-btn" id="railNext" aria-label="Next formats"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 5 16 12 9 19"></polyline></svg></button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rail-nav">
      <span class="rail-hint hint-desktop">Drag, or use the arrows</span>
      <span class="rail-hint hint-mobile">Swipe to explore →</span>
      <div class="rail-progress">
        <div class="rail-track"><div class="rail-fill" id="railFill"></div></div>
        <span class="rail-count"><em id="railCurrent">01</em> / {{ products | length }}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="height: 40px;"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ INDUSTRIES WE SERVE ============ -->
  <section class="industries" id="industries-teaser">
    <div class="sec">
      <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
        <p class="sec-eyebrow">Industries we serve</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title">Seven sectors, <em>one standard.</em></h2>
        <p class="sec-lead">The hygiene, barrier and documentation adapt to the sector. The print quality doesn't.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="acc" id="indAcc" data-reveal>
        {% for s in industries %}<div class="acc-panel{% if loop.first %} is-open{% endif %}" style="--ic:{{ s.accent }};">
          <img class="acc-photo" src="/assets/images/{{ s.image }}.png" alt="{{ s.name }} sector packaging" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="acc-photo-scrim"></div>
          <div class="acc-closed"><span class="acc-num">{{ s.num }}</span><span class="acc-name-v">{{ s.short }}</span></div>
          <div class="acc-open"><span class="acc-num">{{ s.num }}</span><h3>{{ s.name }}</h3><p>{{ s.applications | join(' · ') }}.</p><a class="r-link" href="/industries/{{ s.slug }}/">Explore sector →</a></div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <p class="shelf-hint hint-desktop">Hover a sector to open it</p>
      <p class="shelf-hint hint-mobile">Tap a sector to open it</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ INFRASTRUCTURE ============ -->
  <section class="sec" id="infrastructure">
    <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
      <p class="sec-eyebrow">Infrastructure</p>
      <h2 class="sec-title">60,000+ sq ft in <em>Bharuch, Gujarat.</em></h2>
      <p class="sec-lead">See full specs — press, lamination, slitting and pouching lines. <a href="/infrastructure/" style="color:var(--accent); text-decoration:underline;">Explore the plant →</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="scrolly">
      <div class="scrolly-sticky">
        <div class="sc-stage" id="scStage">
          <figure class="sc-shot is-active" data-shot="1" style="margin:0;">
            <img src="/assets/images/printing-machine.png" alt="9-colour rotogravure printing press" />
            <figcaption>9-colour rotogravure</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="sc-shot" data-shot="2" style="margin:0;">
            <img src="/assets/images/lami.png" alt="Solvent-less lamination machine" />
            <figcaption>Solvent-less lamination</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="sc-shot" data-shot="3" style="margin:0;">
            <img src="/assets/images/slitting-machine.png" alt="Slitting machine" />
            <figcaption>Slitting line</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="sc-shot" data-shot="4" style="margin:0;">
            <img src="/assets/images/pouch.png" alt="Pouching line" />
            <figcaption>Pouching machines</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scrolly-steps">
        <div class="sc-step is-active" data-step="1">
          <figure class="sc-inline" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/printing-machine.png" alt="9-colour rotogravure printing press" loading="lazy" /></figure>
          <p class="sc-num">i</p>
          <h3>9-Colour Rotogravure Press</h3>
          <p>Auto registration and web guiding for precise multi-colour print — deep, repeatable colour across long runs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-step" data-step="2">
          <figure class="sc-inline" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/lami.png" alt="Solvent-less lamination machine" loading="lazy" /></figure>
          <p class="sc-num">ii</p>
          <h3>Solvent-Less &amp; Solvent-Based Lamination</h3>
          <p>Food-safe multi-layer bonding and specialised barrier structures, matched to the product inside.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-step" data-step="3">
          <figure class="sc-inline" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/slitting-machine.png" alt="Slitting machine" loading="lazy" /></figure>
          <p class="sc-num">iii</p>
          <h3>Precision Slitting Lines</h3>
          <p>Tension-controlled winding to exact reel widths, ready for downstream pouching or delivery as film rolls.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-step" data-step="4">
          <figure class="sc-inline" style="margin:0;"><img src="/assets/images/pouch.png" alt="Pouching line" loading="lazy" /></figure>
          <p class="sc-num">iv</p>
          <h3>Centre- &amp; Side-Seal Pouching</h3>
          <p>Finished pouches converted in-house — every format from stand-up to spout, sealed and inspected on line.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ WHY US ============ -->
  <section class="sec" id="why-us">
    <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
      <p class="sec-eyebrow">Why us</p>
      <h2 class="sec-title">What sets us <em>apart.</em></h2>
      <p class="sec-lead">Six reasons brands stay with us past the first order.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-grid stagger" data-reveal>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#b25c2e;">
        <span class="why-glyph" aria-hidden="true">{{ icons.icon('shield') }}</span>
        <h4>Assured Quality</h4>
        <p>ISO 9001:2015 systems and an in-house ASTM lab — eight tests on every batch, full documentation at dispatch.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#c89a3a;">
        <span class="why-glyph" aria-hidden="true">{{ icons.icon('truck') }}</span>
        <h4>On-Time Delivery</h4>
        <p>3–5 week production lead times, honestly quoted and tracked — exporting to 10+ countries via sea freight.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#7a6e3f;">
        <span class="why-glyph" aria-hidden="true">{{ icons.icon('sliders') }}</span>
        <h4>Customized Solutions</h4>
        <p>Structure, size, barrier and finish engineered per product — recommendation within 24 hours of your brief.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#7a8a6c;">
        <span class="why-glyph" aria-hidden="true">{{ icons.icon('gear') }}</span>
        <h4>Advanced Machinery</h4>
        <p>9-colour rotogravure with auto registration, solvent-less lamination, precision slitting and pouching lines.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#3b2a20;">
        <span class="why-glyph" aria-hidden="true">{{ icons.icon('users') }}</span>
        <h4>Skilled Workforce</h4>
        <p>An experienced production and QC team under the Gangamani group's 20+ years of manufacturing discipline.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card" style="--wc:#b25c2e;">
        <span class="why-glyph" aria-hidden="true">{{ icons.icon('recycle') }}</span>
        <h4>100% Recyclable Options</h4>
        <p>Mono-material LLDPE structures for EPR-compliant brands — sustainability without sacrificing shelf appeal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ CLIENTELE ============ -->
  <section class="clientele" id="clientele" aria-label="Our clientele">
    <div class="sec">
      <div class="sec-head" data-reveal>
        <p class="sec-eyebrow">Our clientele</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title">Trusted across sectors <em>and borders.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="client-marquee" data-reveal>
        <div class="client-track">
          {% for i in [1, 2] %}<div class="client-set"{% if i == 2 %} aria-hidden="true"{% endif %}>
            {% for c in clients %}{% if c.text %}<span class="client-badge client-badge-text"><b>{{ c.text }}</b></span>{% else %}<span class="client-badge"><img src="/assets/images/clients/{{ c.img }}.webp" alt="{{ c.name }} logo" loading="lazy" /></span>{% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>{% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="client-note">Trusted by 200+ Indian brands across agrochemical, food, pharma and FMCG — a few of the names we pack for.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ TESTIMONIALS ============ -->
  <section class="sec" aria-label="Testimonials">
    <div class="sec-head" data-reveal><p class="sec-eyebrow">What clients say</p><h2 class="sec-title">Trusted by brands <em>who don't compromise.</em></h2></div>
    <div class="testi-grid" data-reveal>
      <div class="testi-card"><p class="testi-quote">G Flexipack turned our first pouch order around faster than any supplier we'd worked with — and the print quality matched our brand exactly.</p><p class="testi-who"><b>Procurement Lead</b> · Agrochemical brand</p></div>
      <div class="testi-card"><p class="testi-quote">Their team recommended a barrier structure we hadn't considered, and it solved a shelf-life issue we'd been stuck on for months.</p><p class="testi-who"><b>Operations Head</b> · Food &amp; snacks brand</p></div>
      <div class="testi-card"><p class="testi-quote">Reliable lead times, clear communication, and documentation on every batch — exactly what we need for a regulated product.</p><p class="testi-who"><b>Quality Manager</b> · Pharma packer</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% include "partials/inquiry-form.njk" %}
